1
00:00:24,980 --> 00:00:28,500
♪Heavens strike with thunderous wrath♪

2
00:00:28,700 --> 00:00:32,180
♪Mountains and rivers shatter before my eyes♪

3
00:00:32,420 --> 00:00:35,500
♪Endless splendor cultivated through lifetimes♪

4
00:00:35,780 --> 00:00:39,220
♪Turns to dust between my fingers in an instant♪

5
00:00:40,540 --> 00:00:44,100
♪When the line between good and evil is clear♪

6
00:00:44,220 --> 00:00:47,780
♪Countless souls drift into the boundless wilds♪

7
00:00:48,340 --> 00:00:51,340
♪Carrying the spirit fire forward♪

8
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:53,340
♪I defy fate♪

9
00:00:53,580 --> 00:00:56,460
♪Just to remain by your side♪

10
00:00:57,340 --> 00:01:00,740
♪Falling into love's abyss♪

11
00:01:01,180 --> 00:01:04,420
♪Like heavy rain pouring down♪

12
00:01:04,860 --> 00:01:08,300
♪Drunk on romance♪

13
00:01:08,460 --> 00:01:11,980
♪In a blink, love and hate vanish into illusion♪

14
00:01:12,700 --> 00:01:16,060
♪Falling into endless love♪

15
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:19,340
♪Stirring waves upending a lifetime♪

16
00:01:19,620 --> 00:01:22,420
♪Even if this life leads to ruin♪

17
00:01:22,860 --> 00:01:26,460
♪I still choose to be entangled with you♪

18
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:30,100
♪Through all lifetimes♪

19
00:01:30,100 --> 00:01:33,100
[When Destiny Brings The Demon]

20
00:01:33,100 --> 00:01:36,500
[Based on the JJWXC novel "When Destiny Brings The Demon" by Fu Hua]

21
00:01:36,540 --> 00:01:39,500
[Episode 11]
[I think I've Become a Hopeless Romantic]

22
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:40,450
But

23
00:01:41,030 --> 00:01:42,170
why is there

24
00:01:42,190 --> 00:01:43,370
Fengshan bloodline here?

25
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:44,890
The Fengshan Clan

26
00:01:45,190 --> 00:01:47,060
has always pursued bloodline purity.

27
00:01:47,960 --> 00:01:49,090
But over the years,

28
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:50,220
some have

29
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:52,010
defied their elders, run off,

30
00:01:52,750 --> 00:01:54,370
and had children with outsiders.

31
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:57,650
Shi Qianlv

32
00:01:58,720 --> 00:02:01,090
has gone to great lengths to gather people of the Fengshan bloodline.

33
00:02:04,310 --> 00:02:05,580
He is playing a long game.

34
00:02:06,390 --> 00:02:08,810
But what could Shi Qianlv possibly do

35
00:02:10,040 --> 00:02:11,130
with those people?

36
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,570
It's for his own selfish desires.

37
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:19,060
I told you before

38
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:22,130
that people in the Gengchen Celestial Palace are all the same.

39
00:02:23,270 --> 00:02:25,090
They will do anything for cultivation.

40
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:29,220
Right now, we just need to find out

41
00:02:29,670 --> 00:02:31,410
where the Shi family took those children,

42
00:02:31,990 --> 00:02:33,570
and we will know his true motives.

43
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:36,460
But the only one who knows about this

44
00:02:36,670 --> 00:02:38,080
is Master Yan.

45
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:40,050
We have no choice but to wait for his return.

46
00:02:40,830 --> 00:02:42,620
After all, no one even knows where he is.

47
00:02:43,110 --> 00:02:44,020
Why wait?

48
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,740
He will come back to me of his own will.

49
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:51,620
Please elaborate, Grandmaster.

50
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:54,090
I will ruin the Yan Residence

51
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:56,410
in Yan Huan's disguise,

52
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:01,060
and that old man will have no choice but to return.

53
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,410
How does it feel to be used

54
00:03:29,830 --> 00:03:31,220
as a breeding vessel,

55
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,340
living in constant manipulation?

56
00:03:42,390 --> 00:03:43,900
Am I really living at all?

57
00:03:46,830 --> 00:03:49,690
Even when I pretended to be a wastrel lost in wine and women,

58
00:03:51,150 --> 00:03:53,570
my family still refused to leave me alone.

59
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:56,130
Living such a miserable life,

60
00:03:57,590 --> 00:03:59,130
I might as well be dead.

61
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:01,690
I'm nothing more than a walking corpse.

62
00:04:11,270 --> 00:04:12,570
You would rather live in disgrace

63
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:16,500
than die with dignity?

64
00:04:18,830 --> 00:04:19,890
Easy for you to say.

65
00:04:21,960 --> 00:04:23,450
I wanted to end it all, too,

66
00:04:27,030 --> 00:04:28,860
but it's not that easy to take my own life.

67
00:04:31,350 --> 00:04:33,060
You haven't been through what I have.

68
00:04:35,390 --> 00:04:36,420
You won't understand.

69
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:52,100
Once everything is over,

70
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,330
I will end it for you.

71
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:06,210
Then that would be best.

72
00:05:11,230 --> 00:05:15,740
So the Grandmaster wants to cause unrest in the Yan family

73
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:17,980
to lure Master Yan back early?

74
00:05:19,390 --> 00:05:20,770
He makes the plans,

75
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:22,370
and I carry them out.

76
00:05:23,030 --> 00:05:24,180
This is a big project.

77
00:05:24,830 --> 00:05:26,370
I don't think we'll be able

78
00:05:26,390 --> 00:05:28,500
to shop and snack like this again

79
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:29,320
anytime soon.

80
00:05:29,640 --> 00:05:32,500
Tingyan, you are starting to use words

81
00:05:33,230 --> 00:05:34,370
I don't understand again.

82
00:05:35,140 --> 00:05:36,620
Never mind.

83
00:05:38,150 --> 00:05:39,060
Those accessories look great!

84
00:05:39,230 --> 00:05:39,620
Come.

85
00:05:46,390 --> 00:05:46,940
What do you think?

86
00:05:47,590 --> 00:05:48,420
I'll try another one.

87
00:05:53,710 --> 00:05:54,420
This one's nice.

88
00:05:54,790 --> 00:05:55,330
Really?

89
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:59,860
Is that Ye Ruling?

90
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:01,690
- Why is she here? - Let me see. How about this one?

91
00:06:02,270 --> 00:06:04,570
The woman next to her looks like...

92
00:06:04,830 --> 00:06:05,540
Liao Tingyan!

93
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:07,770
Isn't Liao Tingyan already dead?

94
00:06:08,470 --> 00:06:09,420
Let's take a closer look.

95
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:13,210
Between these two,

96
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:14,740
which should I choose?

97
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:22,450
What is it? What are you looking at?

98
00:06:23,710 --> 00:06:24,300
Nothing.

99
00:06:24,790 --> 00:06:26,370
Tingyan, this hairpin is very pretty.

100
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:27,210
I really like it.

101
00:06:27,520 --> 00:06:28,370
Help me pick some more.

102
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:29,620
I will be right back.

103
00:06:35,870 --> 00:06:37,300
Oh no, he's from the Shi family.

104
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:53,890
Canglan?

105
00:06:54,790 --> 00:06:55,540
What are you doing here?

106
00:06:56,440 --> 00:06:57,570
If I hadn't followed you in secret,

107
00:06:58,230 --> 00:06:59,330
I doubt you would've ever told me

108
00:06:59,350 --> 00:07:00,810
that Liao Tingyan was still alive.

109
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:11,010
You used a firefly to track me?

110
00:07:13,590 --> 00:07:14,130
Canglan,

111
00:07:15,230 --> 00:07:16,500
don't do anything to Liao Tingyan.

112
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:19,370
I'm sure there will be a way to have the best of both worlds.

113
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:21,180
How can I count on someone

114
00:07:21,710 --> 00:07:22,920
as soft as you to save our people?

115
00:07:23,390 --> 00:07:24,010
Ye Ruling,

116
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,680
I'll go my own way from here.

117
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:27,010
Let's see who reaches the goal first.

118
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:31,770
What are you doing?

119
00:07:32,080 --> 00:07:32,890
Keeping you in check.

120
00:07:33,230 --> 00:07:34,010
Do you realize

121
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:35,770
that if Sima Jiao catches wind of this,

122
00:07:36,270 --> 00:07:38,540
both of us will end up losing everything?

123
00:07:54,390 --> 00:07:55,770
Mr. Li, you're finally here.

124
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:56,740
This way.

125
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,130
We've been waiting for you.

126
00:08:02,100 --> 00:08:04,660
[Songbird Pavilion]

127
00:08:15,150 --> 00:08:16,500
Sir, you're here.

128
00:08:16,520 --> 00:08:17,180
Go away.

129
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:19,100
Sir...

130
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:20,860
Stop!

131
00:08:24,590 --> 00:08:25,330
Sir...

132
00:08:25,350 --> 00:08:26,130
Go away...

133
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:28,370
What a weird man!

134
00:08:29,710 --> 00:08:31,570
Young Master, maybe we've made a mistake.

135
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,540
Was that really not Liao Tingyan?

136
00:08:35,230 --> 00:08:35,690
Let's go.

137
00:08:38,230 --> 00:08:39,300
That was close.

138
00:08:39,830 --> 00:08:41,210
When did I turn into an otter?

139
00:08:41,990 --> 00:08:43,090
Looks like the Grandmaster is here, too.

140
00:08:45,300 --> 00:08:47,660
[Yan Residence]

141
00:08:58,800 --> 00:09:00,660
Grandmaster, did you step in to protect me just now?

142
00:09:08,870 --> 00:09:09,610
Did you get hurt?

143
00:09:10,870 --> 00:09:11,660
No.

144
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,900
Good thing you were there.

145
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,610
You turned me into an otter just in time,

146
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:17,970
or I would've been spotted and captured by people

147
00:09:17,990 --> 00:09:18,940
from the Shi family.

148
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,260
What happened today feels off.

149
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:24,970
It seems someone has leaked your whereabouts.

150
00:09:36,230 --> 00:09:38,610
Who was with you earlier?

151
00:09:45,230 --> 00:09:46,570
I went out by myself.

152
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,450
Ruling was with me.

153
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,610
You're getting bolder and bolder.

154
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,330
Now you even dare to lie to me.

155
00:10:03,710 --> 00:10:05,300
I was afraid you'd be suspicious

156
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:06,850
of Ruling if I told you the truth.

157
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:08,780
She is, after all, the Mistress of the Yin Palace.

158
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,330
She could be colluding with the Shi family.

159
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:11,810
No,

160
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:14,570
Ruling would never betray me.

161
00:10:14,590 --> 00:10:15,570
I trust her.

162
00:10:15,830 --> 00:10:17,780
Besides, nothing serious happened, right?

163
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,730
It's all been resolved now.

164
00:10:20,230 --> 00:10:21,060
Nothing serious?

165
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,140
I saved your life.

166
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,420
I gave you my blood.

167
00:10:24,830 --> 00:10:25,810
If you're injured or in danger,

168
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:27,380
it wastes my blood.

169
00:10:28,470 --> 00:10:30,610
So the bottom line is you don't want me wasting your blood, huh?

170
00:10:39,510 --> 00:10:40,450
Rotten Sima Jiao,

171
00:10:41,630 --> 00:10:43,020
always trying to scare me.

172
00:10:44,510 --> 00:10:45,020
By the way,

173
00:10:47,510 --> 00:10:48,570
if you're such a good liar,

174
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:51,660
let's see how you're going to trick people now.

175
00:10:59,230 --> 00:11:01,490
Sima Jiao, remove the Truth Spell now!

176
00:11:13,590 --> 00:11:14,180
Mr. Yan,

177
00:11:14,470 --> 00:11:15,490
about Xian...

178
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,810
Hey, say something, will you?

179
00:11:22,590 --> 00:11:24,210
I will find out where they are.

180
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:25,730
Thank you, sir.

181
00:11:28,350 --> 00:11:29,140
Thank you, sir,

182
00:11:29,990 --> 00:11:31,970
for granting me freedom.

183
00:11:32,280 --> 00:11:34,380
You're letting us go because you understand

184
00:11:34,630 --> 00:11:35,900
our suffering, right?

185
00:11:36,510 --> 00:11:38,810
I see today as the day of my rebirth,

186
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:41,730
and I dressed up to welcome it.

187
00:11:41,870 --> 00:11:42,450
That's great.

188
00:11:43,350 --> 00:11:44,540
But this pink outfit

189
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:45,420
doesn't quite brighten you up.

190
00:11:48,350 --> 00:11:50,210
Even when making small talk, I blurt out my real thoughts.

191
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:51,940
It's so embarrassing.

192
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:53,140
How rude of you!

193
00:11:53,830 --> 00:11:55,490
You're in no position to comment on my clothes.

194
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,330
I'm so sorry.

195
00:11:59,630 --> 00:12:00,660
Grandmaster, could you please

196
00:12:00,680 --> 00:12:02,140
remove the Truth Spell for me?

197
00:12:02,560 --> 00:12:04,260
I know people in Chiyan City are at lower realms

198
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:05,730
and can't see the spell mark on my forehead,

199
00:12:05,750 --> 00:12:06,780
but if I keep blurting out

200
00:12:06,800 --> 00:12:07,610
whatever's on my mind,

201
00:12:07,630 --> 00:12:08,970
they're going to think I'm weird.

202
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:09,780
Maybe they'll even

203
00:12:10,560 --> 00:12:12,180
beat me up one day, you know?

204
00:12:13,230 --> 00:12:14,610
As I said, it's a punishment.

205
00:12:15,350 --> 00:12:17,810
If someone's willing to save me the trouble and give you a beating,

206
00:12:19,510 --> 00:12:20,970
that wouldn't be such a bad thing.

207
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:24,090
What kind of schoolkid behavior is that?

208
00:12:24,510 --> 00:12:26,300
So you're pleased with what I did,

209
00:12:26,750 --> 00:12:28,090
since you called me a "schoolkid."

210
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:31,610
"Schoolkid" isn't a compliment.

211
00:12:31,830 --> 00:12:34,450
It means you're childish, petty, and ridiculous...

212
00:12:36,040 --> 00:12:38,210
Liao Tingyan, shut your mouth already!

213
00:12:38,590 --> 00:12:39,450
At this point,

214
00:12:40,230 --> 00:12:41,850
you might as well keep going.

215
00:12:43,040 --> 00:12:45,060
I wouldn't dare...

216
00:12:45,590 --> 00:12:47,210
I said that because you made me.

217
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:48,850
If you remove the spell,

218
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:52,020
I'll shower you with all the flattery you want.

219
00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:55,660
Fake flattery is boring.

220
00:12:56,110 --> 00:12:57,090
I have no interest in it.

221
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,420
Greetings, sir.

222
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:04,380
Sir, may I stay here?

223
00:13:04,680 --> 00:13:05,730
I have no one else to rely on.

224
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:07,610
I'm willing to stay and serve you day and night.

225
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:08,450
No need.

226
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,660
I'm not used to having someone around.

227
00:13:12,160 --> 00:13:12,780
Isn't that right?

228
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:14,450
You seem pretty used to it to me.

229
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:16,260
You fell asleep with me in your arms last night.

230
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:22,020
So you sent us away

231
00:13:22,280 --> 00:13:23,490
because of this young lady?

232
00:13:23,920 --> 00:13:24,450
That's right.

233
00:13:25,710 --> 00:13:27,420
She's the only one I want by my side.

234
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:30,940
Happy?

235
00:13:32,040 --> 00:13:34,970
"Happy" isn't the word. More like shocked.

236
00:13:35,830 --> 00:13:37,060
Where are you going with this?

237
00:13:37,510 --> 00:13:38,660
This wasn't in the script.

238
00:13:39,560 --> 00:13:41,020
I think you're so secretly delighted

239
00:13:41,830 --> 00:13:43,260
that you're starting to babble nonsense.

240
00:13:45,750 --> 00:13:47,380
Lady, I'll tell you the truth.

241
00:13:47,510 --> 00:13:49,330
I'm actually an otter,

242
00:13:49,590 --> 00:13:51,780
and he's not the real Mr. Yan. I...

243
00:13:52,560 --> 00:13:53,380
What she means is

244
00:13:54,230 --> 00:13:56,020
that I no longer wish to be Young Master Yan,

245
00:13:56,960 --> 00:13:58,810
and that I want to live by my own rules.

246
00:14:00,230 --> 00:14:01,300
I get it.

247
00:14:01,680 --> 00:14:03,940
I will forever pray for happiness for you and the young lady.

248
00:14:06,590 --> 00:14:08,540
See? If you don't lift the spell,

249
00:14:08,560 --> 00:14:09,810
it'll backfire

250
00:14:10,230 --> 00:14:11,810
and ruin your grand plan.

251
00:14:12,560 --> 00:14:14,090
I don't know about any "grand plan."

252
00:14:15,160 --> 00:14:18,090
All I know is someone called me a schoolkid.

253
00:14:22,280 --> 00:14:24,420
And the Truth Spell will last another five days.

254
00:14:29,630 --> 00:14:31,450
Are you cursing me in your head right now?

255
00:14:31,630 --> 00:14:32,210
Yes.

256
00:14:36,800 --> 00:14:37,900
Then I'll add another five days.

257
00:14:46,710 --> 00:14:48,090
So you're giving me a taste

258
00:14:48,110 --> 00:14:49,210
of my own medicine

259
00:14:49,710 --> 00:14:50,940
by trapping me here?

260
00:14:54,590 --> 00:14:56,090
Stay here and reflect on what you did.

261
00:14:57,440 --> 00:14:59,330
And stop thinking about parting ways with me.

262
00:15:03,230 --> 00:15:04,140
I will find a way

263
00:15:04,590 --> 00:15:06,260
to earn Sima Jiao's trust quickly.

264
00:15:08,110 --> 00:15:09,610
I won't let our plan be hindered.

265
00:15:11,110 --> 00:15:11,780
You'll find a way?

266
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:14,260
You've been in Chiyan City for days

267
00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:16,380
and still haven't figured out how to activate

268
00:15:16,400 --> 00:15:18,260
Liao Tingyan's extreme-cold nature, have you?

269
00:15:23,990 --> 00:15:25,060
I've hit the mark, haven't I?

270
00:15:26,400 --> 00:15:28,780
Ruling, stop fooling yourself.

271
00:15:29,470 --> 00:15:31,260
At this point, our only option is to take

272
00:15:31,800 --> 00:15:32,900
Liao Tingyan's core.

273
00:15:36,830 --> 00:15:37,570
There is another option.

274
00:15:38,800 --> 00:15:39,900
Kill Sima Jiao.

275
00:15:41,230 --> 00:15:44,570
Easier said than done. Do you even realize what he's capable of?

276
00:15:45,160 --> 00:15:46,140
You don't stand a chance.

277
00:15:46,710 --> 00:15:47,810
An opportunity will come.

278
00:15:51,750 --> 00:15:52,300
Ruling,

279
00:15:53,560 --> 00:15:56,140
please, get your priorities straight.

280
00:16:10,280 --> 00:16:10,780
Grandmaster.

281
00:16:18,510 --> 00:16:20,020
Did you tell the Shi family

282
00:16:20,040 --> 00:16:20,970
where Liao Tingyan was?

283
00:16:21,510 --> 00:16:22,810
I have never revealed

284
00:16:22,920 --> 00:16:23,940
a single word to anyone.

285
00:16:28,710 --> 00:16:30,660
Then why did you come to Chiyan City looking for us?

286
00:16:31,350 --> 00:16:33,490
I was worried about Tingyan's safety,

287
00:16:34,230 --> 00:16:36,730
and I didn't believe you had truly killed her.

288
00:16:37,510 --> 00:16:38,610
So I resorted

289
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:41,210
to using a firefly to track her down.

290
00:16:48,710 --> 00:16:49,610
Please forgive me, Grandmaster.

291
00:16:51,560 --> 00:16:53,450
If I find out you have divided loyalties,

292
00:16:54,160 --> 00:16:55,380
I will kill you without hesitation.

293
00:16:56,470 --> 00:16:57,060
I would not dare.

294
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:12,620
I wonder what Mr. Yan is up to today.

295
00:17:12,840 --> 00:17:13,940
First, he dismissed all the concubines.

296
00:17:14,360 --> 00:17:16,820
Then he ordered everyone to take inventory of Master Yan's property.

297
00:17:17,230 --> 00:17:18,100
It's pretty alarming.

298
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:22,290
Miss, I heard from a concubine who left the residence

299
00:17:22,510 --> 00:17:23,580
that Mr. Yan was very fond of you.

300
00:17:24,840 --> 00:17:25,940
We're both servants here.

301
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:29,340
- Could you put in a good word for me, your big brother... - Big brother?

302
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:32,770
And help me become a steward or something?

303
00:17:33,120 --> 00:17:34,730
If there's anything you need in the future,

304
00:17:35,030 --> 00:17:35,580
I'll help you, too.

305
00:17:36,120 --> 00:17:37,420
Thank you, big brother.

306
00:17:37,920 --> 00:17:40,250
But judging by your looks, you're more like my uncle.

307
00:17:40,470 --> 00:17:41,730
I'm only in my early twenties.

308
00:17:42,440 --> 00:17:43,210
I'm so sorry.

309
00:17:43,680 --> 00:17:45,450
I saw your receding hairline

310
00:17:45,470 --> 00:17:46,660
and thought you were over 50...

311
00:17:47,470 --> 00:17:49,340
Sorry, I mean no offense.

312
00:17:49,360 --> 00:17:50,940
I'll let it slide for Mr. Yan's sake!

313
00:17:51,840 --> 00:17:52,620
You're so rude!

314
00:17:57,230 --> 00:17:57,690
Miss?

315
00:18:02,550 --> 00:18:03,530
Sore throat?

316
00:18:04,310 --> 00:18:05,140
Maybe you're just too tired.

317
00:18:05,230 --> 00:18:05,970
Get some rest.

318
00:18:05,990 --> 00:18:06,660
I'll get back to work.

319
00:18:11,750 --> 00:18:13,490
Can everyone please stop talking to me?

320
00:18:14,230 --> 00:18:16,180
I've offended so many people in just one day.

321
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:26,690
Grandmaster.

322
00:18:35,750 --> 00:18:36,820
What are you doing?

323
00:18:40,070 --> 00:18:41,210
Looks like it's working.

324
00:18:41,550 --> 00:18:42,660
I don't have to worry anymore.

325
00:18:42,920 --> 00:18:44,340
If I can't hear, I don't have to answer.

326
00:18:46,070 --> 00:18:46,940
Interesting,

327
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:48,380
Liao Tingyan.

328
00:18:48,790 --> 00:18:51,050
Whether you praise me or scold me,

329
00:18:51,070 --> 00:18:53,050
- I can't hear you. - There's a pond behind you.

330
00:18:57,920 --> 00:18:58,620
You don't

331
00:18:58,640 --> 00:19:00,340
actually think this makes you look good, do you?

332
00:19:08,030 --> 00:19:09,140
You did that on purpose, didn't you?

333
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:10,620
You're trying to mess with me.

334
00:19:10,990 --> 00:19:12,340
I warned you

335
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:14,050
there was a pond behind you.

336
00:19:14,840 --> 00:19:15,690
You didn't listen.

337
00:19:16,270 --> 00:19:17,180
What could I do?

338
00:19:18,550 --> 00:19:20,010
You're going to such lengths

339
00:19:20,440 --> 00:19:21,860
just to amuse me now.

340
00:19:22,070 --> 00:19:22,970
And you've been putting

341
00:19:23,680 --> 00:19:26,140
a lot of effort into playing tricks on me today, schoolkid.

342
00:19:26,840 --> 00:19:27,620
If you want to keep this up,

343
00:19:27,990 --> 00:19:28,860
I'm all in.

344
00:19:29,750 --> 00:19:30,340
So do you?

345
00:19:32,200 --> 00:19:32,770
No.

346
00:19:32,990 --> 00:19:33,820
Pull me up.

347
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:09,420
Let's go have some fun with the steward here.

348
00:20:15,310 --> 00:20:15,860
Sir,

349
00:20:16,470 --> 00:20:19,050
Master Yan's belongings are all here.

350
00:20:22,270 --> 00:20:24,010
Go to the bank and take all the money out.

351
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:25,450
Well...

352
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:27,250
And tell the servants outside

353
00:20:27,750 --> 00:20:29,900
they can take whatever they want from the chests

354
00:20:30,270 --> 00:20:31,340
in the courtyard.

355
00:20:32,070 --> 00:20:33,380
Then they can leave the residence.

356
00:20:33,750 --> 00:20:34,420
Sir,

357
00:20:35,070 --> 00:20:37,380
those are Master Yan's most prized treasures.

358
00:20:37,600 --> 00:20:38,180
I...

359
00:20:40,550 --> 00:20:41,420
Understood.

360
00:20:53,070 --> 00:20:54,620
What is Mr. Yan trying to do?

361
00:20:55,310 --> 00:20:57,140
I wonder where Master Yan is now.

362
00:20:58,030 --> 00:20:58,620
This won't do.

363
00:20:58,960 --> 00:21:00,770
I must send someone to get the news to him at once.

364
00:21:01,030 --> 00:21:02,340
Hopefully, when he hears it,

365
00:21:02,680 --> 00:21:03,530
he will hurry back.

366
00:21:14,030 --> 00:21:15,970
There are no jewels, gold, or silver

367
00:21:15,990 --> 00:21:17,290
in these chests.

368
00:21:17,710 --> 00:21:19,100
How come they're the most popular?

369
00:21:19,200 --> 00:21:19,660
Miss,

370
00:21:20,120 --> 00:21:21,250
