371
00:21:21,790 --> 00:21:23,380
People in this city are mostly at low realms,

372
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:25,530
but Master Yan is a great admirer of immortal arts.

373
00:21:25,960 --> 00:21:27,620
These are all magical artifacts he has collected

374
00:21:27,790 --> 00:21:28,970
from all over the Celestial Palace.

375
00:21:29,270 --> 00:21:29,940
Magical artifacts?

376
00:21:29,960 --> 00:21:30,420
Yes.

377
00:21:31,070 --> 00:21:31,730
Look.

378
00:21:32,030 --> 00:21:32,860
This is the Sound Channeler,

379
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:33,620
and this

380
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:34,530
is the Mirror of Reversal.

381
00:21:34,880 --> 00:21:35,420
It can

382
00:21:36,120 --> 00:21:37,730
briefly reflect the opponent's spells back at them.

383
00:21:38,470 --> 00:21:39,010
This is a pair

384
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:39,970
of Lovebond Plaques.

385
00:21:40,230 --> 00:21:41,450
If you carve

386
00:21:41,470 --> 00:21:42,380
two people's names on them,

387
00:21:42,750 --> 00:21:43,970
the two will fall in love.

388
00:21:45,880 --> 00:21:48,050
I've long been infatuated with a pleasure house's top courtesan.

389
00:21:48,310 --> 00:21:51,730
I plan to carve both our names on them.

390
00:21:51,750 --> 00:21:52,730
The top courtesan?

391
00:21:53,160 --> 00:21:54,660
I don't think you're worthy of her.

392
00:21:56,840 --> 00:21:58,050
You... You've gone too far!

393
00:21:58,070 --> 00:21:58,730
Sorry.

394
00:21:58,750 --> 00:21:59,970
I didn't mean to say that out loud.

395
00:22:00,640 --> 00:22:01,620
I'll apologize.

396
00:22:01,840 --> 00:22:03,010
When I apologize, I mean it, too!

397
00:22:03,030 --> 00:22:03,860
I don't want to hear it!

398
00:22:06,600 --> 00:22:07,530
When is Sima Jiao

399
00:22:07,550 --> 00:22:09,100
going to lift the Truth Spell?

400
00:22:13,920 --> 00:22:15,010
Mirror of Reversal?

401
00:22:21,200 --> 00:22:21,820
Sima Jiao,

402
00:22:22,360 --> 00:22:23,010
we need to talk.

403
00:22:25,680 --> 00:22:26,580
About what?

404
00:22:27,070 --> 00:22:28,490
How much longer do you plan to let

405
00:22:28,510 --> 00:22:29,970
the Truth Spell make a fool out of me?

406
00:22:30,440 --> 00:22:32,180
Could you please remove it?

407
00:22:32,510 --> 00:22:33,380
It's really causing

408
00:22:33,400 --> 00:22:34,660
serious trouble in my life.

409
00:22:37,920 --> 00:22:38,940
Do you admit you were wrong?

410
00:22:39,880 --> 00:22:40,490
Why did you

411
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:42,730
lie to me in the first place?

412
00:22:44,470 --> 00:22:45,580
I've already explained.

413
00:22:45,600 --> 00:22:46,730
I had my reasons.

414
00:22:46,990 --> 00:22:48,620
Why do you have to force me to tell the truth?

415
00:22:49,070 --> 00:22:51,180
What's wrong with wanting a little privacy?

416
00:22:51,550 --> 00:22:52,730
I can't even keep my own thoughts

417
00:22:52,750 --> 00:22:53,660
