418
00:22:53,920 --> 00:22:54,900
It's really exhausting!

419
00:23:17,070 --> 00:23:18,900
I can't stand empty pleasantries

420
00:23:20,920 --> 00:23:21,970
and lies,

421
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:26,730
so I don't want anyone

422
00:23:28,230 --> 00:23:29,770
to hide anything from me.

423
00:23:29,780 --> 00:23:33,540
♪No one reaches, no one hears...♪

424
00:23:34,510 --> 00:23:35,490
Grandmaster.

425
00:23:37,540 --> 00:23:41,620
♪Fall like fireworks...♪

426
00:23:41,640 --> 00:23:44,690
I know you've always been surrounded by lies.

427
00:23:46,030 --> 00:23:47,970
I know deception makes you feel lonely.

428
00:23:49,880 --> 00:23:50,490
But what about me?

429
00:23:51,470 --> 00:23:52,730
In this world,

430
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:56,250
everything feels unfamiliar to me,

431
00:23:56,270 --> 00:23:57,620
and no one understands me.

432
00:23:59,460 --> 00:24:03,020
♪Even if my very soul were to vanish...♪

433
00:24:04,200 --> 00:24:05,580
The truth is, we're both lonely.

434
00:24:08,120 --> 00:24:10,730
But can we not try to read

435
00:24:10,990 --> 00:24:12,450
each other's mood this way?

436
00:24:13,510 --> 00:24:15,030
There are many ways to know

437
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:16,690
what someone truly thinks.

438
00:24:17,460 --> 00:24:23,300
♪Mad love blooms a lotus in the heart...♪

439
00:24:24,030 --> 00:24:24,770
So please,

440
00:24:26,030 --> 00:24:28,660
stop punishing and tormenting me.

441
00:24:30,230 --> 00:24:31,380
You can't keep making me

442
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:34,210
so uncomfortable just because it's fun.

443
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:41,250
So you think

444
00:24:43,270 --> 00:24:44,620
I'm doing this for fun?

445
00:24:45,310 --> 00:24:46,050
What else could it be?

446
00:24:47,510 --> 00:24:48,690
For the bigger picture?

447
00:24:49,070 --> 00:24:50,420
To make sure your plans don't fail?

448
00:24:52,700 --> 00:24:56,220
♪Snow not gone, flame not out♪

449
00:24:56,260 --> 00:24:59,140
♪Prism of three lifetimes♪

450
00:24:59,820 --> 00:25:04,420
♪You, untouched by moon's regrets♪

451
00:25:06,620 --> 00:25:09,780
♪No one reaches, no one hears...♪

452
00:25:09,790 --> 00:25:11,290
The most upsetting part

453
00:25:14,120 --> 00:25:15,050
is that everything you just said

454
00:25:17,510 --> 00:25:19,050
is exactly what you really think.

455
00:25:20,440 --> 00:25:22,860
Then why don't you tell me what you really think?

456
00:25:23,020 --> 00:25:25,780
♪Memories fade♪

457
00:25:25,820 --> 00:25:28,060
♪We wander the mortal world in search...♪

458
00:25:30,160 --> 00:25:31,210
I want to hear the truth.

459
00:25:32,180 --> 00:25:35,780
♪Cycle back to raging flames♪

460
00:25:35,820 --> 00:25:39,340
♪Even if my very soul were to vanish...♪

461
00:25:40,920 --> 00:25:41,580
I'm doing this

462
00:25:45,790 --> 00:25:47,180
because I cherish you so much...

463
00:25:49,340 --> 00:25:53,300
♪I would never regret the day I met you...♪

464
00:25:53,840 --> 00:25:55,690
...that I don't want you to be harmed in the slightest.

465
00:26:00,260 --> 00:26:10,820
♪Mad love blooms a lotus in the heart...♪

466
00:26:20,070 --> 00:26:20,770
If you dare use

467
00:26:21,470 --> 00:26:23,340
such foolish trinkets on me again,

468
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:26,290
you'll be an otter for the rest of your life.

469
00:26:35,470 --> 00:26:37,420
What on earth did Sima Jiao mean by that?

470
00:26:38,470 --> 00:26:39,450
Could it be

471
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:42,340
that he has romantic feelings

472
00:26:43,270 --> 00:26:44,490
for me?

473
00:26:45,750 --> 00:26:46,340
No...

474
00:26:46,680 --> 00:26:47,380
Someone like him

475
00:26:47,400 --> 00:26:48,660
couldn't possibly fall for anyone, right?

476
00:26:49,680 --> 00:26:51,210
But that look in his eyes

477
00:26:51,600 --> 00:26:53,860
was so sincere.

478
00:26:55,310 --> 00:26:57,010
Ugh, I'm so confused.

479
00:27:18,750 --> 00:27:19,420
You're drunk.

480
00:27:19,920 --> 00:27:20,970
Impossible.

481
00:27:21,230 --> 00:27:23,010
I can hold my liquor.

482
00:27:23,030 --> 00:27:24,580
I've only had one cup.

483
00:27:24,680 --> 00:27:25,770
How could I be drunk?

484
00:27:26,030 --> 00:27:27,010
You were human before,

485
00:27:27,920 --> 00:27:29,140
but now you're an otter.

486
00:27:30,270 --> 00:27:31,290
Your tolerance is naturally different.

487
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:40,060
Did you prepare all this food for yourself?

488
00:27:42,990 --> 00:27:43,690
Who else could it be?

489
00:27:45,550 --> 00:27:46,050
Well,

490
00:27:46,470 --> 00:27:48,380
I prepared it to celebrate us freeing

491
00:27:48,400 --> 00:27:50,140
most of the people in the Yan Residence.

492
00:27:51,550 --> 00:27:53,940
Grandmaster, you should join me.

493
00:28:04,960 --> 00:28:05,820
What are you doing?

494
00:28:06,550 --> 00:28:08,900
Sleeping with my body pillow.

495
00:28:09,270 --> 00:28:10,690
Don't you also like holding me

496
00:28:10,710 --> 00:28:12,730
in your sleep when I'm a little otter?

497
00:28:12,990 --> 00:28:14,860
What, are you shy?

498
00:28:22,360 --> 00:28:23,210
Who said I'm shy?

499
00:28:31,680 --> 00:28:33,180
Even the Truth Spell can't rein you in.

500
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:36,660
You lifted it?

501
00:28:38,120 --> 00:28:39,690
Thank you, my dear Grandmaster!

502
00:28:40,070 --> 00:28:42,690
My mood has finally gone from cloudy to sunny!

503
00:28:46,230 --> 00:28:46,820
Your mood?

504
00:28:50,400 --> 00:28:51,820
The truth is, we're both lonely.

505
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:54,490
But can we not try to read

506
00:28:54,510 --> 00:28:55,970
each other's mood this way?

507
00:28:57,270 --> 00:28:57,900
I feel

508
00:28:58,960 --> 00:29:00,730
like my mind has been taken over by something strange.

509
00:29:02,070 --> 00:29:03,730
Have I become what she called

510
00:29:05,070 --> 00:29:05,970
a "hopeless romantic"?

511
00:29:07,160 --> 00:29:10,100
Are you the only one from Serene Vale who likes making up

512
00:29:10,230 --> 00:29:11,140
words and phrases?

513
00:29:12,990 --> 00:29:15,900
What does "dear" mean?

514
00:29:16,550 --> 00:29:19,820
It's a polite, universal form of address.

515
00:29:20,750 --> 00:29:23,690
I usually use it for people I'm close to.

516
00:29:24,040 --> 00:29:25,340
But it can also be

517
00:29:25,360 --> 00:29:27,040
for the most annoying clients.

518
00:29:31,750 --> 00:29:33,380
There are many ways to know

519
00:29:33,880 --> 00:29:34,970
what someone truly thinks.

520
00:29:37,420 --> 00:29:41,860
♪Falling into endless love. Stirring waves♪

521
00:29:41,900 --> 00:29:44,380
♪Upending a lifetime...♪

522
00:29:46,160 --> 00:29:47,900
So do you see me as the former

523
00:29:49,230 --> 00:29:50,050
or the latter?

524
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:53,690
Of course I don't hate you.

525
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:56,250
No lie. That's the truth.

526
00:30:01,960 --> 00:30:02,660
The truth, huh?

527
00:30:05,070 --> 00:30:06,290
Are you feeling unwell?

528
00:30:09,160 --> 00:30:09,770
No.

529
00:30:13,310 --> 00:30:15,450
Drink this, and you'll sober up.

530
00:30:17,400 --> 00:30:18,690
I'm too lazy to drink it myself.

531
00:30:20,580 --> 00:30:25,500
♪I defy fate just to remain by your side...♪

532
00:30:27,360 --> 00:30:27,820
Here.

533
00:30:30,540 --> 00:30:33,260
♪Pouring down♪

534
00:30:33,620 --> 00:30:38,020
♪Drunk on romance. In a blink♪

535
00:30:38,060 --> 00:30:41,260
♪Love and hate vanish into illusion...♪

536
00:30:41,470 --> 00:30:44,530
