537
00:30:45,780 --> 00:30:48,260
♪Upending a lifetime♪

538
00:30:48,300 --> 00:30:51,300
♪Even if this life leads to ruin...♪

539
00:30:54,230 --> 00:30:56,210
Why are you looking at me

540
00:30:56,230 --> 00:30:57,420
with such a happy smile?

541
00:31:04,990 --> 00:31:05,690
When did I

542
00:31:07,070 --> 00:31:08,380
smile at you?

543
00:31:11,070 --> 00:31:11,770
You're imagining things.

544
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:14,530
I'm leaving.

545
00:31:14,880 --> 00:31:16,290
Guess I was overthinking it.

546
00:31:16,790 --> 00:31:18,970
Sima Jiao is still the same cold man.

547
00:31:19,840 --> 00:31:20,900
Grandmaster, where are you going?

548
00:31:21,360 --> 00:31:21,900
To kill someone.

549
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:24,050
Is that your catchphrase?

550
00:31:24,990 --> 00:31:26,530
Grandmaster, don't be rash!

551
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:45,380
Have you come to take my life?

552
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:46,860
Exactly.

553
00:31:53,710 --> 00:31:54,690
Grandmaster, a word, please.

554
00:31:56,160 --> 00:31:56,770
What are you doing?

555
00:31:58,510 --> 00:32:01,940
Grandmaster, the person you want to kill is Mr. Yan?

556
00:32:02,790 --> 00:32:03,530
What's wrong with that?

