00:32:04,550 --> 00:32:05,770
The news of a son's death is probably

558
00:32:06,160 --> 00:32:07,690
the most effective way to lure that old man back.

559
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:12,690
Can we not be so violent?

560
00:32:12,990 --> 00:32:15,340
Can't we handle this a little more humanely?

561
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:20,450
For him, this would be a kind of release.

562
00:32:20,750 --> 00:32:22,420
How can death be a release?

563
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:24,050
Isn't there another way?

564
00:32:26,360 --> 00:32:27,380
Then what do you suggest?

565
00:32:41,030 --> 00:32:43,250
Just stop him from being used

566
00:32:43,270 --> 00:32:44,010
as a breeding vessel.

567
00:32:44,960 --> 00:32:47,180
Why don't we help him elope with Ms. Qing'er?

568
00:32:47,270 --> 00:32:48,690
That would still hinder the Yan family's plan

569
00:32:48,710 --> 00:32:50,340
to strengthen the Fengshan bloodline.

570
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:51,860
And Master Yan would still return.

571
00:33:04,200 --> 00:33:07,490
You want to drag Mr. Yan out of the mire?

572
00:33:09,680 --> 00:33:10,660
Don't bother.

573
00:33:11,750 --> 00:33:13,180
It will only be a waste of effort.

574
00:33:15,920 --> 00:33:16,940
Where there's a will, there's a way.

575
00:33:17,990 --> 00:33:19,180
I believe we can do it.

576
00:33:19,990 --> 00:33:22,340
Trust me, Grandmaster.

577
00:33:31,550 --> 00:33:33,490
You really won't turn back until you hit a wall.

578
00:33:34,070 --> 00:33:35,530
We won't know until we try.

579
00:33:36,200 --> 00:33:37,940
I'll go help Ms. Qing'er get ready, then.

580
00:33:39,120 --> 00:33:39,820
Have you heard?

581
00:33:39,920 --> 00:33:42,180
Mr. Yan suddenly dismissed all his concubines

582
00:33:42,200 --> 00:33:44,100
and gave each one a huge relocation fee.

583
00:33:45,030 --> 00:33:46,940
He gave each of them a relocation fee?

584
00:33:47,070 --> 00:33:48,010
It's true!

585
00:33:48,360 --> 00:33:48,770
No.

586
00:33:48,990 --> 00:33:50,420
He formally divorced them.

587
00:33:50,840 --> 00:33:51,820
Not only that,

588
00:33:52,230 --> 00:33:54,420
he even divided up the family assets among the servants

589
00:33:54,840 --> 00:33:56,490
and let them all go.

590
00:33:56,840 --> 00:33:57,450
Really?

591
00:33:58,600 --> 00:34:00,860
I knew it. Things are a complete mess now.

592
00:34:01,200 --> 00:34:03,290
What do you think he's up to?

593
00:34:03,710 --> 00:34:06,180
Why is Mr. Yan suddenly acting so recklessly?

594
00:34:06,400 --> 00:34:07,100
I don't get it.

595
00:34:11,440 --> 00:34:12,380
Have you heard?

596
00:34:12,880 --> 00:34:14,860
Mr. Yan is planning to elope with Ms. Qing'er, a courtesan

597
00:34:14,960 --> 00:34:17,340
he used to secretly meet at the pleasure house.

598
00:34:18,320 --> 00:34:20,780
He's thrown away everything in the Yan family for her.

599
00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:22,450
- Is that true? - Of course it is.

600
00:34:22,590 --> 00:34:24,610
When Master Yan returns, there will be a real show to watch.

601
00:34:24,800 --> 00:34:25,530
Definitely.

602
00:34:30,220 --> 00:34:33,020
[Yan Residence]

603
00:34:34,860 --> 00:34:37,500
[Master Yan]

604
00:34:48,960 --> 00:34:49,820
What has gotten into you?

605
00:34:50,840 --> 00:34:51,780
I heard while I was away

606
00:34:51,800 --> 00:34:53,260
that you'd been making a mess at home!

607
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:00,970
You squandered the family fortune

608
00:35:01,670 --> 00:35:02,570
and dismissed all your concubines,

609
00:35:03,400 --> 00:35:04,610
and now you want to elope with a courtesan?

610
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:06,170
If you keep this up,

611
00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:08,260
how will the matter I entrusted to you ever move forward?

612
00:35:08,960 --> 00:35:09,570
What matter?

613
00:35:10,550 --> 00:35:11,490
Tell me.

614
00:35:14,510 --> 00:35:16,740
You actually forgot what I told you?

615
00:35:18,030 --> 00:35:18,940
Useless fool!

616
00:35:21,110 --> 00:35:22,300
Those cheap women out there

617
00:35:22,320 --> 00:35:23,420
have completely bewitched you.

618
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:24,530
Listen,

619
00:35:24,760 --> 00:35:26,380
from now on, you're not allowed to go out again!

620
00:35:27,070 --> 00:35:28,860
I'll get you a few more concubines

621
00:35:29,150 --> 00:35:30,340
so you can have more children.

622
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:31,380
Otherwise,

623
00:35:31,590 --> 00:35:33,260
our family will be in misery,

624
00:35:33,630 --> 00:35:34,780
and you won't live in comfort either!

625
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:36,340
Who

626
00:35:36,670 --> 00:35:37,700
are those children for?

627
00:35:37,990 --> 00:35:38,940
You...!

628
00:35:41,110 --> 00:35:42,490
Has the pleasure house

629
00:35:43,030 --> 00:35:44,220
rotted your brain?

630
00:35:44,590 --> 00:35:46,450
You haven't even called me Father once since you came in.

631
00:35:46,800 --> 00:35:47,740
You're a disgrace!

632
00:35:50,360 --> 00:35:51,610
You want me to call you Father?

633
00:35:52,360 --> 00:35:54,380
I don't think you deserve that kind of respect yet.

634
00:35:54,550 --> 00:35:54,970
You!

635
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:01,530
Who are you?

636
00:36:02,400 --> 00:36:03,340
You're not my son.

637
00:36:06,500 --> 00:36:07,770
I am your ancestor.

638
00:36:08,230 --> 00:36:10,350
Insolent brat, how dare you insult me?

639
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:19,610
Tell me the truth behind the flame-shaped birthmark

640
00:36:21,150 --> 00:36:22,170
on Yan Huan's back.

641
00:36:22,800 --> 00:36:27,130
The Yan family and the Sima clan both belong to the Fengshan lineage.

642
00:36:27,800 --> 00:36:29,090
Every few generations,

643
00:36:29,320 --> 00:36:31,780
someone in the Yan family is born with Sima blood,

644
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:34,700
and they will have that flame-shaped birthmark on their back.

645
00:36:35,440 --> 00:36:36,900
And what do you do with such people?

646
00:36:37,550 --> 00:36:39,050
When a child like that is born,

647
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:42,380
they will immediately be sent to that place.

648
00:36:42,840 --> 00:36:44,700
If their bloodline power is strong enough,

649
00:36:44,990 --> 00:36:46,300
they will stay there permanently,

650
00:36:46,670 --> 00:36:49,170
and our family will be rewarded with great benefits.

651
00:36:50,070 --> 00:36:51,420
If their power is weaker,

652
00:36:51,960 --> 00:36:53,420
like my son Yan Huan's,

653
00:36:53,720 --> 00:36:55,220
they will be allowed to return home.

654
00:36:56,110 --> 00:36:57,130
What is that place?

655
00:36:57,800 --> 00:36:58,530
Baifeng Mountain.

656
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:00,260
Where is it?

657
00:37:01,110 --> 00:37:01,740
I don't know.

658
00:37:02,630 --> 00:37:04,260
Emissaries come to pick them up.

659
00:37:04,670 --> 00:37:05,700
We can't go near.

660
00:37:06,190 --> 00:37:07,260
We can only stay outside.

661
00:37:13,240 --> 00:37:15,260
If I want to get to Baifeng Mountain quickly,

662
00:37:16,400 --> 00:37:17,260
how do I do that?

663
00:37:17,550 --> 00:37:18,380
You'll have to wait.

664
00:37:18,920 --> 00:37:21,380
The emissaries from Baifeng Mountain contact us, not the other way around.

665
00:37:21,720 --> 00:37:22,530
At the end of each month,

666
00:37:23,030 --> 00:37:24,170
they come

667
00:37:24,670 --> 00:37:27,170
to the residence to check for pregnancies.

668
00:37:27,720 --> 00:37:29,090
If there's a newborn,

669
00:37:29,550 --> 00:37:32,090
they will examine

670
00:37:32,510 --> 00:37:34,900
whether the child belongs to the Fengshan bloodline.

671
00:37:35,510 --> 00:37:36,650
If they do,

672
00:37:36,960 --> 00:37:38,570
they will be taken to Baifeng Mountain immediately,

673
00:37:39,510 --> 00:37:41,740
and I will go along as well.

674
00:37:46,240 --> 00:37:47,970
So all that is needed is a child?

675
00:37:50,440 --> 00:37:51,340
Not a problem at all.

676
00:37:53,360 --> 00:37:54,820
Have you memorized

677
00:37:55,030 --> 00:37:55,970
everything I taught you?

678
00:37:55,990 --> 00:37:57,050
I even practice it in my sleep.

679
00:38:01,670 --> 00:38:02,300
Grandmaster.

680
00:38:02,720 --> 00:38:03,220
Nianjiu,

681
00:38:03,630 --> 00:38:05,340
after you keep Master Yan confined in the residence,

682
00:38:05,550 --> 00:38:06,780
I need you to do something else for me.

683
00:38:08,190 --> 00:38:09,700
You can refuse politely

684
00:38:09,720 --> 00:38:10,740
by saying...

685
00:38:11,590 --> 00:38:12,050
Uh...

686
00:38:13,400 --> 00:38:14,380
This doesn't look right.

687
00:38:17,440 --> 00:38:18,170
What did you say?

688
00:38:18,720 --> 00:38:20,010
How is it wrong to do something for me?

689
00:38:21,030 --> 00:38:22,700
If the other person insists,

690
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:23,970
just keep declining politely

691
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:25,050
by saying...

692
00:38:25,400 --> 00:38:26,260
I don't have the time.

693
00:38:27,920 --> 00:38:29,420
And if I tell you to make time?

694
00:38:30,760 --> 00:38:32,260
Then you can be more direct

695
00:38:32,400 --> 00:38:33,420
and give a firm refusal.

696
00:38:34,720 --> 00:38:35,530
No, I can't.

697
00:38:36,030 --> 00:38:36,640
Nianjiu,

698
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:39,220
are you tired of living or something?

699
00:38:40,280 --> 00:38:41,970
What kind of poison have you been feeding him?

700
00:38:44,110 --> 00:38:44,900
My apologies, Grandmaster.

701
00:38:46,590 --> 00:38:47,260
I just

702
00:38:48,440 --> 00:38:49,860
taught him a few ways

703
00:38:49,880 --> 00:38:51,130
of speaking and dealing with people.

704
00:38:51,960 --> 00:38:53,700
You mean you taught him how to betray his Grandmaster?

705
00:38:54,630 --> 00:38:55,340
I wouldn't dare.

706
00:38:56,240 --> 00:38:57,450
That's quite an accusation.

707
00:38:57,470 --> 00:38:57,970
Grandmaster,

708
00:38:58,960 --> 00:39:00,420
this really has nothing to do with Ruling.

709
00:39:00,760 --> 00:39:02,340
I was the one pestering her to teach me

710
00:39:02,760 --> 00:39:03,970
how to be a better person.

711
00:39:04,760 --> 00:39:05,940
The first lesson I learned

712
00:39:06,240 --> 00:39:07,380
from her

713
00:39:07,400 --> 00:39:08,610
was how to say no to people,

714
00:39:09,320 --> 00:39:10,090
because I wanted

715
00:39:10,550 --> 00:39:12,050
to stop acting

716
00:39:12,960 --> 00:39:14,340
like some domesticated animal,

717
00:39:14,590 --> 00:39:16,700
obedient to everyone about everything.

718
00:39:22,960 --> 00:39:24,010
Instead of learning from her,

719
00:39:24,880 --> 00:39:26,900
you should have come to me to learn how to be a person.

720
00:39:30,320 --> 00:39:30,970
Grandmaster,

721
00:39:31,240 --> 00:39:33,050
stop giving Nianjiu a hard time.

722
00:39:33,800 --> 00:39:35,340
I need to go find Mr. Yan now.

723
00:39:35,670 --> 00:39:37,080
Why don't you turn me back into a human?

724
00:39:41,470 --> 00:39:42,050
Tingyan.

725
00:39:44,070 --> 00:39:44,860
You're toast.

726
00:39:44,880 --> 00:39:46,420
So the otter was Tingyan?

727
00:39:49,510 --> 00:39:50,170
In a few days,

728
00:39:50,550 --> 00:39:52,220
I'll be going to Baifeng Mountain with Master Yan.

729
00:39:52,670 --> 00:39:53,450
Return to keep watch

730
00:39:53,760 --> 00:39:55,570
on the Shi family and the Eight Palaces for me.

731
00:39:55,990 --> 00:39:57,130
If anything unusual happens,

732
00:39:57,320 --> 00:39:58,340
report to me immediately.

733
00:39:58,360 --> 00:39:58,860
Understood.

734
00:39:59,400 --> 00:40:00,740
If I can make a contribution to this

735
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:02,090
and gain Sima Jiao's trust,

736
00:40:02,630 --> 00:40:04,570
then whether I choose to kill or use him later,

737
00:40:04,990 --> 00:40:05,570
I may be able

738
00:40:05,960 --> 00:40:07,900
to break the Immortal-Demon Barrier faster.

739
00:40:09,400 --> 00:40:09,970
Grandmaster,

740
00:40:10,190 --> 00:40:11,420
let me go with Nianjiu.

741
00:40:15,510 --> 00:40:16,010
Fine.

742
00:40:17,550 --> 00:40:18,570
Report to me immediately

743
00:40:19,190 --> 00:40:20,340
if anything happens.

744
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:21,970
Understood.

745
00:40:42,240 --> 00:40:43,090
Mr. Yan.

746
00:40:46,440 --> 00:40:47,490
Please come with me.

747
00:40:47,800 --> 00:40:49,570
Ms. Qing'er and your daughter are waiting for you.

748
00:40:51,320 --> 00:40:51,780
No,

749
00:40:53,030 --> 00:40:53,700
I'm not going.

750
00:40:54,720 --> 00:40:55,610
I can't put them in danger.

751
00:40:56,960 --> 00:40:58,170
They'd be better off

752
00:40:58,720 --> 00:41:00,050
staying far away from me.

753
00:41:03,550 --> 00:41:04,700
Pull yourself together.

754
00:41:05,150 --> 00:41:07,380
Your father has told us about Baifeng Mountain.

755
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:09,130
My Grand...

756
00:41:12,550 --> 00:41:14,300
My young master is very powerful.

757
00:41:14,590 --> 00:41:16,420
You can count on him to take care of things there

758
00:41:16,590 --> 00:41:18,010
and ensure your safety.

759
00:41:18,240 --> 00:41:20,570
We've already paved the way for you.

760
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:22,450
From now on, you can live however you want.

761
00:41:23,280 --> 00:41:24,570
How can I possibly live a carefree life

762
00:41:26,070 --> 00:41:27,650
after going through something like this?

763
00:41:28,510 --> 00:41:30,090
The Fengshan bloodline

764
00:41:31,920 --> 00:41:33,380
will one day drag me back

765
00:41:33,400 --> 00:41:34,740
into tragedy.

766
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:37,740
He's right.

767
00:42:14,380 --> 00:42:16,180
♪Autumn winds sigh♪

768
00:42:16,260 --> 00:42:17,980
♪Moon and stars dapple the sky♪

769
00:42:18,180 --> 00:42:21,580
♪Brushing the loneliness of bygone days♪

770
00:42:22,220 --> 00:42:23,940
♪Candlelight flickers low♪

771
00:42:24,180 --> 00:42:26,140
♪Shadows sway♪

772
00:42:26,420 --> 00:42:29,580
♪Shimmering in the night♪

773
00:42:30,180 --> 00:42:31,860
♪With a brush I draw♪

774
00:42:32,260 --> 00:42:34,060
♪The color of light♪

775
00:42:34,220 --> 00:42:37,740
♪To warm your frozen soul♪

776
00:42:38,220 --> 00:42:39,940
♪Memories anchor here♪

777
00:42:40,060 --> 00:42:42,060
♪Longing is engraved♪

778
00:42:42,420 --> 00:42:45,140
♪Yet cannot be touched♪

779
00:42:45,620 --> 00:42:47,780
♪Following♪

780
00:42:48,140 --> 00:42:50,180
♪The veins of gravel♪

781
00:42:50,540 --> 00:42:53,220
♪I turn into spirit fire♪

782
00:42:54,260 --> 00:42:55,700
♪Burning away♪

783
00:42:56,140 --> 00:43:01,500
♪All these karmic ties♪

784
00:43:02,220 --> 00:43:03,940
♪To save you♪

785
00:43:04,420 --> 00:43:05,980
♪To save me♪

786
00:43:06,460 --> 00:43:09,380
♪To cross over all suffering, I'll break through♪

787
00:43:10,340 --> 00:43:12,100
♪The laws of heaven♪

788
00:43:12,580 --> 00:43:14,060
♪The vortex of reincarnation♪

789
00:43:14,380 --> 00:43:17,940
♪What of life and death?♪

790
00:43:18,540 --> 00:43:20,100
♪To save you♪

791
00:43:20,340 --> 00:43:22,140
♪To save me♪

792
00:43:22,300 --> 00:43:25,580
♪To redeem all beings, I'll let pass♪

793
00:43:26,180 --> 00:43:28,060
♪Right and wrong♪

794
00:43:28,220 --> 00:43:29,980
♪Rumors and tales♪

795
00:43:30,300 --> 00:43:33,620
♪To seize fate♪

796
00:43:34,220 --> 00:43:36,820
♪With my own hands♪

797
00:43:38,380 --> 00:43:40,060
♪For you♪

798
00:43:40,420 --> 00:43:42,060
♪For me♪

799
00:43:42,580 --> 00:43:45,460
♪For the healing of wounds♪

800
00:43:46,140 --> 00:43:47,980
♪I'll stir the murky seas♪

801
00:43:48,260 --> 00:43:49,980
♪And strive against the heavens♪

802
00:43:50,580 --> 00:43:53,580
♪To protect the vastness♪

803
00:43:54,140 --> 00:43:55,540
♪For you♪

804
00:43:56,220 --> 00:43:57,740
♪For me♪

805
00:43:58,100 --> 00:44:01,140
♪For the light of dawn♪

806
00:44:01,940 --> 00:44:03,580
♪I'll face promises♪

807
00:44:04,020 --> 00:44:05,620
♪Like a moth to a flame♪

808
00:44:06,300 --> 00:44:09,220
♪And use my body to shine♪

809
00:44:13,460 --> 00:44:17,300
♪On even more♪
